{"tid":330671,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【電影改詞】［Her 觸不到的她］同 Siri 拍拖，每日生活要點過？","createTime":"2017-07-21T12:14:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T10:44:05.000Z","uid":39666,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"04a5850217a6ea3f24e3397c8816a728ef5212f6","tid":330671,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T12:14:23.000Z","msg":"連登巴絲打你哋好，第一次 post 完整改詞上嚟，還望各位多多指教。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無諗過，世上最了解你喜好同需要嘅，可能係你部電話？<br />\n又有無諗過，再發展落去，未來佢可能係你最理想嘅情人？<br />\n佢可以廿四小時陪住你，同你傾計，可以叫你起身返工，甚至幫你處理一大堆瑣碎嘢。<br />\n噉樣嘅完美關係，你有無興趣試下？<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n**<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">聽歌請按此</span></strong>：<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tsUg0kWqTt4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtsUg0kWqTt4&d=FvFA8ojCvdVcNNfXNVqDUXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=c596fd10\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tsUg0kWqTt4</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>雲端情人</strong> <span style=\"color: teal;\">（原曲：攝氏零度）</span><br />\n<br />\n填詞：雪人<br />\n編曲：Felix Chan<br />\n主唱：二進制<br />\n插畫：Mercury Chung</span><br />\n<br />\n疏遠了的愛　冷落前塵內<br />\n進步了幾代　人類到底化不開<br />\n編製哪種愛　能讓我覓到伴侶給我下載<br />\n修復過　訊息錯誤亦能改<br />\n<br />\n或我從來不被愛<br />\n血肉浪遊在迷霧蒼海<br />\n得你隨時候命伴我輕鬆跨障礙<br />\n沿路放聲喝采<br />\n<br />\n如意識隔著雲端<br />\n談何為愛在殘喘<br />\n誰鬧市裡蕩迴兜圈<br />\n伴侶配合同時公轉<br />\n<br />\n完美也只因你太懂計算<br />\n已把我孤單的那份疲倦　都看穿<br />\n早清楚軀殼永無存<br />\n唯獨是你的聲線動人　帶溫暖<br />\n<br />\n虛構某些愛　寄住鐵盒內<br />\n領導了將來　同步更貌似分開<br />\n操控哪些愛　連共處亦靠自己單向上載<br />\n多合襯　也不過獨步人海<br />\n<br />\n如意識隔著雲端<br />\n談何為愛在殘喘<br />\n誰鬧市裡蕩迴兜圈<br />\n伴侶配合同時公轉<br />\n<br />\n完美也只因你太懂計算<br />\n已把我孤單的那份疲倦　都看穿<br />\n早清楚軀殼永無存<br />\n唯獨是你的聲線動人　帶溫暖<br />\n<br />\n就算效能提升　高速串流場景<br />\n看遍地球名勝　光纖卻絕情<br />\n就算定期調整　安裝更多人性<br />\n你卻未曾驗證　空虛那共鳴<br />\n<br />\n如意識隔著雲端<br />\n談何為愛在殘喘<br />\n誰鬧市裡蕩迴兜圈<br />\n伴侶配合同時公轉<br />\n<br />\n如你已注定離遠　怎抱怨<br />\n要逼我孤單得更是疲倦　心更酸<br />\n觸不到的你卻猶存<br />\n重頭在擷取虛擬劇情　再依眷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s12.postimg.org/tmpmosh99/image.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs12.postimg.org%2Ftmpmosh99%2Fimage.png&h=b3e2acab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74c5b21bde080f714f946d4c0d69960670b4bcc6","tid":330671,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T12:16:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"079fc7de64be188b05ff4fa4290c4cddbe097850","tid":330671,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T12:17:08.000Z","msg":"如果巴打們有興趣睇小弟鳩噏，可以參觀一下小弟嘅 page 同 ig 啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nFacebook：<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/HornySnowman\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHornySnowman&d=FvFA8ojCvdVcNNfXNVqDUXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=6cb7bd33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/HornySnowman</a><br />\nInstagram：＠hornysnowmanhk<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">( ig 好快會有嘢睇，好似係）</span></span>"},{"pid":"717aa258700b4bc1c3a5537f3451626350858016","tid":330671,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T12:24:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"589d850e75fb1beeee987356bd2fdfe00e594fbc","tid":330671,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T12:35:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf1b3b28f8a8846a555ecf574359ca05499a0639","tid":330671,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T12:41:44.000Z","msg":"戲同歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.